41
00:41:33,260 --> 00:41:34,400
Scenario 1 is niks veranderen.

42
00:41:34,639 --> 00:41:35,639
Scenario 2 is inzetten op...

43
00:41:35,799 --> 00:41:37,279
quick wins.

